snippet.title: Star Farmer: Warlock of the Universe | Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
In this relaxing bullet heaven, farming adventure, play as a powerful Warlock who has a side hustle harvesting plants in space.

Get Star Farmer: Warlock of the Universe now on Steam!
